tags.description:
### The availability slots response

The successful response comes in three variants.

- If it does find slots, `times` will be non-empty and `next_available_date` will be null;

- If it does not find slots in the primary range but it does find on the search range, then `times` will be empty and `next_available_date` will be not-null;

- If it does not find slots in any range, then `times` will be empty and `next_available_date` will be null.

```
{
  slots: [
    {
      times: [String],
      date: Date,
      id: String
    }
  ],
  next_available_date: null | Date
}
```
